Description
-----------

Shows surfaces using the editor image instead of the actual texture.

Usage
-----

At the console type...

    r_showEditorImages [flag]

Parameters
----------

-   [flag]
    -   0 - Render textures as usual.
    -   1 - Use the image defined with
        [qer\_editorimage](Qer_editorimage_%28Material_global_keyword%29 "Qer editorimage (Material global keyword)")
        global keyword instead.

